Package io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2

Class MsdxContainer.Builder<T>

java.lang.Object
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.MsdxContainer.Builder<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
MsdxRecord.Builder
Enclosing class:
MsdxContainer<T>
public static class MsdxContainer.Builder<T>
extends java.lang.Object
Builder for MsdxContainer. The builder can be used to verify the data against a predefined Schema or to create the Schema. Normally, for data Containers, the Schema is specified by the constructor. If the Container is used for a Schema, do not specify a Schema.

Direct use of this builder is discouraged. Instead, use the builders in MsdxSchema or MsdxRecord.
